"title": "8136: knowing God, effects of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8136",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Knowing God has a transforming effect on a person spiritually and morally and makes that person bold in actions for God. Not knowing God in the present will result in dissatisfaction and degeneration into wickedness and in the future will bring eternal alienation from him.</p>\n<h2>The effects of knowing God</h2>\n<h3>Spiritual transformation: from death to life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:9\">COL 1:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:3\">JHN 17:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:8-Gal4:9\">GAL 4:8–4:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:17\">EPH 1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:19\">EPH 3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:2\">COL 2:2</a></p>\n<h3>Moral transformation: from evil to good</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:1-Prov2:6\">PRO 2:1–2:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:5\">2CO 10:5</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:3-1Thess4:5\">1TH 4:3–4:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:26\">ROM 16:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:17-Eph4:24\">EPH 4:17–4:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:9-Phil1:11\">PHP 1:9–1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:10\">COL 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:10\">1JN 3:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:8\">1JN 4:8</a></p>\n<h3>Boldness of action for God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:38-Jer32:39\">JER 32:38–32:39</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:32\">DAN 11:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps138:3\">PSA 138:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:1\">PRO 28:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:8-Acts6:10\">ACT 6:8–6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:12\">2CO 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:13\">1PE 1:13</a></p>\n<h2>Biblical images of knowing God</h2>\n<h3>Like parent and child</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:14\">2SA 7:14</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr17:13\">1CH 17:13</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:1\">1JN 3:1</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:6\">HEB 12:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:12\">PRO 3:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:5\">DEU 8:5</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:7\">PSA 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:10\">PSA 27:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:5\">PSA 68:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:26\">PSA 89:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:13\">PSA 103:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:15\">ISA 49:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:12-Isa66:13\">ISA 66:12–66:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:1\">HOS 11:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:45\">MAT 5:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:48\">MAT 5:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:6-Matt6:9\">MAT 6:6–6:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:18\">MAT 6:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:32\">MAT 6:32</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:11-Luke15:32\">LUK 15:11–15:32</a> <em>the parable of the lost son</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:21\">JHN 14:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:3\">1CO 1:3</a></p>\n<h3>Like husband and wife</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:5\">ISA 62:5</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:14\">JER 3:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:5\">ISA 54:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:2\">JER 2:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:20\">JER 3:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:32\">JER 31:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos2:16\">HOS 2:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:25\">EPH 5:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:7\">REV 19:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:2\">REV 21:2</a></p>\n<h3>Like king and subject</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:1\">PSA 97:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam8:7\">1SA 8:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps5:2\">PSA 5:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:16\">PSA 10:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:10\">PSA 29:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps44:4\">PSA 44:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps84:3\">PSA 84:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:3\">PSA 95:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps99:1\">PSA 99:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:1\">PSA 145:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:33\">MAT 6:33</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:31\">LUK 12:31</a> <em>Jesus Christ's teaching on seeking first his kingdom</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:17\">1TI 1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:15\">1TI 6:15</a></p>\n<h3>Like shepherd and sheep</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen48:15\">GEN 48:15</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:1-Ps23:2\">PSA 23:1–23:2</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:11\">ISA 40:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps28:9\">PSA 28:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps80:1\">PSA 80:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:16\">EZK 34:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:14\">MIC 7:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:11\">JHN 10:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:17\">REV 7:17</a></p>\n<h2>The peril of not knowing God</h2>\n<h3>Lack of satisfaction and degeneration in the present</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:21-Rom1:32\">ROM 1:21–1:32</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:15-Titus1:16\">TIT 1:15–1:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod5:2\">EXO 5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:22\">JER 4:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:2-Rom10:3\">ROM 10:2–10:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:3-1Thess4:5\">1TH 4:3–4:5</a></p>\n<h3>Eternal punishment in the future</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:22-Matt7:23\">MAT 7:22–7:23</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:18-Rom1:19\">ROM 1:18–1:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:5\">ROM 2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:8\">2TH 1:8</a></p>",
